Package android.gameengine.icadroids.input

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MotionSensor
    Motion Sensor is used to receive certain statics about certain motionEvent note that this only works on real phones and not in emulator.
    OnScreenButton
    An custom (android) imageButton used in the onScreenButtons.
    OnScreenButtons
    This class provides statics and a few function to easily make use of the touch functionality of an android device.
    TouchInput
    TouchInput class that sets and handles the input and put the result in easy-to-use flags.
